常意外，询问道：「你今天是来推业务的吗？」他还让一旁的同事收下了孩子手中的资料，并告诉孩子：「你未来一定比你爸干得更好，我好好考察一下你爸的公司，如果你爸干得好，我给你爸打广告，干得不好我吐槽你爸。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d82fef03ad5706ce41d5e8e08c76d12b_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037126627788838360"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4efi5JiS1sNREAMaCTExOTQ2MTY4NiDkj4XQBjAAOKwBQBtyEzIwMzcxMjY2Mjc3ODg4MzgzNjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1778692591.710004", "card_id": "Q_2037205187375231742", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 155}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "博主发现老年人不走天桥、选择横穿马路，可能是因为台阶行走吃力，这类困境普遍吗？有办法帮他们安全通行吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[2 张图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-992a7b22d785cccdaa3c69dc2d9c1469_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037205187375231742"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4efi5JiS1sNREAMaCTExOTQ2NjI1MiCOoobQBjAAOJcCQBxyEzIwMzcyMDUxODczNzUyMzE3NDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1778692591.710491", "card_id": "Q_2031930574454137517", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待在哈佛大学物理学教授 Schwartz 指导下，Claude 完成高能物理论文？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "论文地址：Resummation of the C-Parameter Sudakov Shoulder Using Effective Field Theory 研究经过（原文）：研究经过（译文）：人工智能最终会代替数学家或理论物理学家吗？ 在这篇论文中，Claude 提出了一种新的分解定理。用教授的话说，在理论物理里，这种定理并不多，每一个都会让我们对量子场论的理解更深一层，而且它做出了可以被实验检验的物理预测。 原本需要教授做几个月的项目在 AI 搬砖下只用了两周。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-95cdce001724fe1d086f5370f3258429_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热